# Places API (New) key for address autocomplete in the location field's
# "Search" mode. Create in Google Cloud Console for this Firebase project,
# restrict by HTTP referrer to your domain(s) — this key is bundled into the
# client build, so it's meant to be public and secured by referrer restriction,
# not kept secret. Leave blank to disable search mode (text mode still works).
VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=
